videos.description: Trevor Lawrence pump fakes and delivers a 16-yard yard touchdown to Amari Rodgers to put Clemson up first.

videos.headline: Lawrence dekes Cuse defense, fires TD to Rodgers

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence keeps it himself on a run-pass option and walks in untouched for a score, his second touchdown of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence strolls into end zone for 2nd TD) 2019/9/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence strolls into end zone for 2nd TD

videos.description: Tim Green, who is battling ALS, is honored at halftime by Syracuse with the retiring of his No. 72. Green is the first Orange defensive player with his number retired.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Syracuse retires Tim Green's No. 72) 2019/9/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Syracuse retires Tim Green's No. 72

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence is picked off deep in Clemson territory and ties his 2018 interception total with his fourth of the season.

videos.headline: Lawrence throws 4th INT of season

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence whips a quick pass to Amari Rodgers, who throws down a defender and tiptoes up the sideline for an 87-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rodgers tightropes sideline on 87-yard TD from Lawrence) 2019/9/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rodgers tightropes sideline on 87-yard TD from Lawrence

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence's errant pass is intercepted by Trill Williams, who returns it 41 yards to the Clemson 3-yard line.

videos.headline: Lawrence's 2nd pick is nearly brought back for 6

videos.description: Syracuse fails to find the end zone for the fourth time in the red zone as Clemson stonewalls Tommy DeVito on his QB keeper.

videos.headline: Clemson stuffs Cuse again in red zone with turnover on downs

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence floats a prayer into the corner of the end zone and is reeled in by Frank Ladson Jr. for a 7-yard touchdown.
